javascriptConfig.javaScript: function MainPage(request, extra, javascriptConfig, output) { this.request = request; this.extra = extra; this.javascriptConfig = javascriptConfig; this.output = output;}function ModuleRequest(url, method, headers, httpBody) { this.url = url; this.method = method; this.headers = headers; this.httpBody = httpBody;}function Output(cellDesing, orientation, defaultLayout, paging, section, layout, data) { this.cellDesing = cellDesing; this.orientation = orientation; this.defaultLayout = defaultLayout; this.paging = paging; this.section = section; this.layout = layout; this.data = data;}function Data(image, title, description, field1, field2, field3, field4, isChapter, link) { this.image = image; this.title = title; this.description = description; this.field1 = field1; this.field2 = field2; this.field3 = field3; this.field4 = field4; this.isChapter = isChapter; this.link = link;}let emptyKeyValue = [{key: '', value: ''}];let results = [];let elements = document.querySelectorAll('.gallery a.cover');for (let element of elements) {let image = element.querySelector('img').getAttribute('data-src');let link = element.href;let title = element.getAttribute('title');results.push(new Data(image, title, '', '', '', '', '', false, new ModuleRequest(link, 'get', emptyKeyValue, null)));}let output = [];output.push(new Output('wide11', 'vertical', 'longTripletsFull', 'none', {sectionName: 'Latest Uploads', separator: false}, null, results));let MainPageObject = new MainPage(new ModuleRequest('', 'get', emptyKeyValue, null), null, {removeJavascript: true, loadInWebView: false, javaScript: ''}, output);document.getElementById('ketsu-final-data').innerHTML = JSON.stringify(MainPageObject);

function Search(request, extra, separator, javascriptConfig, output) { this.request = request; this.extra = extra; this.separator = separator; this.javascriptConfig = javascriptConfig; this.output = output;}function ModuleRequest(url, method, headers, httpBody) { this.url = url; this.method = method; this.headers = headers; this.httpBody = httpBody;}function Output(cellDesing, orientation, defaultLayout, paging, section, layout, data) { this.cellDesing = cellDesing; this.orientation = orientation; this.defaultLayout = defaultLayout; this.paging = paging; this.section = section; this.layout = layout; this.data = data;}function Data(image, title, description, field1, field2, field3, field4, isChapter, link) { this.image = image; this.title = title; this.description = description; this.field1 = field1; this.field2 = field2; this.field3 = field3; this.field4 = field4; this.isChapter = isChapter; this.link = link;}let emptyKeyValue = [{key: '', value: ''}];let results = [];let elements = document.querySelectorAll('.gallery a.cover');for (let element of elements) {let image = element.querySelector('img').getAttribute('data-src');let link = element.href;let title = element.getAttribute('title');results.push(new Data(image, title, '', '', '', '', '', false, new ModuleRequest(link, 'get', emptyKeyValue, null)));}let output = [];output.push(new Output('wide11', 'vertical', 'longTripletsFull', 'none', {sectionName: 'Search Results', separator: false}, null, results));let SearchPageObject = new Search(new ModuleRequest('', 'get', emptyKeyValue, null), null, '', {removeJavascript: true, loadInWebView: false, javaScript: ''}, output);document.getElementById('ketsu-final-data').innerHTML = JSON.stringify(SearchPageObject);

function Info(request, extra, javascriptConfig, output) { this.request = request; this.extra = extra; this.javascriptConfig = javascriptConfig; this.output = output;}function ModuleRequest(url, method, headers, httpBody) { this.url = url; this.method = method; this.headers = headers; this.httpBody = httpBody;}function Output(image, title, description, field1, field2, field3, field4, chapters) { this.image = image; this.title = title; this.description = description; this.field1 = field1; this.field2 = field2; this.field3 = field3; this.field4 = field4; this.chapters = chapters;}function Chapter(chapName, link) { this.chapName = chapName; this.link = link;}let emptyKeyValue = [{key: '', value: ''}];let image = document.querySelector('#cover img').src;let title = document.querySelector('#info h1').textContent.trim();let description = '';let genres = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#tags .tag-container span.name')).map(e => e.textContent.trim());let chapters = [];let images = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.thumb-container img')).map(e => new ModuleRequest(e.getAttribute('data-src'), 'get', emptyKeyValue, null));for (let i = 0; i < images.length; i++) { chapters.push(new Chapter(`Page ${i + 1}`, images[i]));}let output = new Output(new ModuleRequest(image, 'get', emptyKeyValue, null), title, description, genres.join(', '), '', '', '', chapters);let InfoPageObject = new Info(new ModuleRequest('', 'get', emptyKeyValue, null), null, {removeJavascript: true, loadInWebView: false, javaScript: ''}, output);document.getElementById('ketsu-final-data').innerHTML = JSON.stringify(InfoPageObject);

function Chapters(request, extra, javascriptConfig, output) { this.request = request; this.extra = extra; this.javascriptConfig = javascriptConfig; this.output = output;}function ModuleRequest(url, method, headers, httpBody) { this.url = url; this.method = method; this.headers = headers; this.httpBody = httpBody;}function Output(images) { this.images = images;}let emptyKeyValue = [{key: '', value: ''}];let images = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.thumb-container img')).map(e => new ModuleRequest(e.getAttribute('data-src'), 'get', emptyKeyValue, null));let chaptersObject = new Chapters(new ModuleRequest('', 'get', emptyKeyValue, null), null, {removeJavascript: true, loadInWebView: false, javaScript: ''}, new Output(images));document.getElementById('ketsu-final-data').innerHTML = JSON.stringify(chaptersObject);
